"title": "5457: power, human",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5457: power, human",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All human power and authority comes from God. God also gives special power to his people.</p>\n<h2>All human power comes from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:1\">ROM 13:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:12\">JDG 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:3\">2KI 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:5\">2KI 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:8\">2CH 25:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37\">DAN 2:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:29-Dan4:32\">DAN 4:29–4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:10-John19:11\">JHN 19:10–19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:28\">ACT 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16\">COL 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:13-1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>God gives power to his people</h2>\n<h3>God's power is at work in believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:35\">PSA 68:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:29-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:29–40:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:7\">2CO 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:9\">2CO 12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:20\">EPH 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10\">EPH 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:11\">COL 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:11\">2TH 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of God giving power to believers</h3>\n<p>Moses:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:21\">EXO 4:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:12\">DEU 34:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:22\">ACT 7:22</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:10\">2SA 5:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr11:9\">1CH 11:9</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:46\">1KI 18:46</a> <em>Elijah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr27:6\">2CH 27:6</a> <em>Jotham</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:23\">DAN 2:23</a> <em>Daniel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:17\">LUK 1:17</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1\">LUK 9:1</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:7\">MRK 6:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:19\">LUK 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:7\">ACT 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8\">ACT 6:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:10\">1CO 12:10</a></p>\n<h3>God gives resurrection power to believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:19-Eph1:20\">EPH 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:4\">2CO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:29\">COL 1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:12\">COL 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit equips individuals for special tasks</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a> <em>Othniel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:6\">1SA 11:6</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a> <em>the Messiah, fulfilled in Jesus Christ (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18\">Lk 4:18</a>)</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a> <em>Micah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:35\">LUK 1:35</a> <em>Mary</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:14\">LUK 4:14</a> <em>Jesus Christ</em></p>\n<h3>The Holy Spirit gives power to believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:49\">LUK 24:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Human power derives from wisdom</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:19\">ECC 7:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:27\">PRO 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:14\">PRO 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:5\">PRO 24:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:13-Eccl9:18\">ECC 9:13–9:18</a></p>\n<h2>The abuse of human power</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:28\">PRO 28:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:2\">JDG 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:7\">JOB 21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:12\">PRO 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:27-Jer5:28\">JER 5:27–5:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:10\">JER 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:6\">EZK 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1\">MIC 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:3\">MIC 7:3</a></p>\n<h2>The absence of human power</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:32\">DEU 28:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:11\">2CH 14:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:5\">NEH 5:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:15-Job5:16\">JOB 5:15–5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:11-Job6:13\">JOB 6:11–6:13</a></p>\n<h2>The power of the wicked is temporary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:16-Ps37:17\">PSA 37:16–37:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:1\">EST 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:32-Ps37:33\">PSA 37:32–37:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7\">PRO 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:20-Ezek13:21\">EZK 13:20–13:21</a></p>",
